item.title: Deltascape source question
item.dc:creator: @Bballguy36 Bballguy36
item.description:
@Bballguy36 wrote:

Okay. Fixing this problem is easy. Go into the source file and right-click the file “run” or whatever it says. Click “edit.” You should see a notepad document pop up. At the end of the document, add the word “pause.” Now save it and exit out. Double-click on the “run” file again and it should work fine. =]
